mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes the articles entitled: SQUARE DANCES "Don't Just Stand", "Bye Bye, My Baby (Grand Square)", and "Shoot the Owl". ROUND DANCES "Busybody", and "Shadow Waltz". SPECIAL FEATURES "Story of a Successful State Organization (Oklahoma)", and "Caller and Sound, Part II". REGULAR FEATURES "As I See It", "Events Seen Thru the Square Dancers' Eye", "'Round the Outside Ring", "From the Floor", and "Square of the Month". PERSONALITIES "The Fred Collettes". THE GREEN SHEET.
